<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row page-header">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <ol class="breadcrumb">
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li>Bootstraps komponenter</li>
        <li class="active">Knappar</li>
      </ol>
      <h1>Formulär</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>(function(e,t,n){var r=e.querySelectorAll("html")[0];r.className=r.className.replace(/(^|\s)no-js(\s|$)/,"$1js$2")})(document,window,0);</script>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-12">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-block">
          <h3 class="card-title">Formulärmönster</h3>
          <blockquote class="blockquote">
            <p class="m-b-0">Life is short. No one wants to fill out a form. Be conversational.</p>
            <footer class="blockquote-footer"><a href="https://uxdesign.cc/design-better-forms-96fadca0f49c#.xx4so5nfm">Design Better Forms (uxdesign.cc)</a></footer>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
          <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row m-b-3">
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <h5>Grundstruktur</h5>
                <p>Formulär layoutas nästa exakt så som Bootstraps egna exempel är uppbyggda. Tanken är även att vi ska försöka följa alla Dos and Don'ts från
                  artikeln <a href="https://uxdesign.cc/design-better-forms-96fadca0f49c#.xx4so5nfm">Design Better Forms (uxdesign.cc)</a>.
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-8">
                <form>
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="exampleInputEmail1">Mailadress</label>
                    <input type="email" class="form-control" id="exampleInputEmail1" aria-describedby="emailHelp" placeholder="Mailadress">
                    <small id="emailHelp" class="form-text text-muted">Korta hjälptexter placeras under inputen inuti en <code>&lt;small class="form-text text-muted"&gt;&lt;/small&gt;</code>.</small>
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="exampleInputPassword1">Lösenord</label>
                    <input type="password" class="form-control" id="exampleInputPassword1" placeholder="Lösenord">
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="exampleInputPassword1">Telefonnummer</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="exampleInputPassword1" placeholder="071-234 56 78">
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="exampleSelect1">Example select</label>
                    <select class="form-control" id="exampleSelect1">
                      <option>1</option>
                      <option>2</option>
                      <option>3</option>
                      <option>4</option>
                      <option>5</option>
                      <option>6</option>
                      <option>7</option>
                      <option>8</option>
                    </select>
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="exampleTextarea">Example textarea <span class="text-muted">- Ej obligatoriskt</span></label>
                    <textarea class="form-control" id="exampleTextarea" rows="3"></textarea>
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group row">
                    <label for="exampleSelect2" class="col-xs-12 col-form-label">Födelsedatum</label>
                    <div class="col-xs-4">
                      <select class="form-control" id="exampleSelect2">
                        <option>Dag</option>
                      </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-4">
                      <select class="form-control" id="exampleSelect3">
                        <option>Månad</option>
                      </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-4">
                      <select class="form-control" id="exampleSelect4">
                        <option>År</option>
                      </select>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="exampleInputPassword1">Gatuadress</label>
                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="exampleInputPassword1" placeholder="Gatuadress">
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group row">
                    <div class="col-xs-8">
                      <label for="exampleInputPassword1">Ort</label>
                      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="exampleInputPassword1" placeholder="Ort">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xs-4">
                      <label for="exampleInputPassword1">Postnummer</label>
                      <input type="text" class="form-control" id="exampleInputPassword1" placeholder="">
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <input type="file" name="file-6[]" id="exampleInputFile" class="inputfile form-control-file" aria-describedby="fileHelp">
                    <label for="exampleInputFile">
                      <a type="button" class="btn btn-secondary"><i class="fa fa-upload fa-fw"></i> <span>Ladda upp fil</span></a>
                    </label>
                    <small id="fileHelp" class="form-text text-muted">This is some placeholder block-level help text for the above input. It's a bit lighter and easily wraps to a new line.</small>
                  </div>
                  <fieldset class="form-group">
                    <legend>Radio buttons</legend>
                    <div class="radio">
                      <label>
                        <input type="radio" name="optionsRadios" id="optionsRadios1" value="option1" checked>
                        Option one is this and that&mdash;be sure to include why it's great
                      </label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="radio">
                      <label>
                        <input type="radio" name="optionsRadios" id="optionsRadios2" value="option2">
                        Option two can be something else and selecting it will deselect option one
                      </label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="radio disabled">
                      <label>
                        <input type="radio" name="optionsRadios" id="optionsRadios3" value="option3" disabled>
                        Option three is disabled
                      </label>
                    </div>
                  </fieldset>
                  <div class="checkbox">
                    <label>
                      <input type="checkbox"> Check me out
                    </label>
                  </div>
                  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Spara ändringar</button>
                  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-secondary">Ångra</button>
                </form>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row m-b-3">
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <h5>Obligatoriska/valfria fält</h5>
                <p>Markera inte obligatoriska fält med en asterisk (*).
                  Lägg istället till en <code>&lt;span class="text-muted"&gt;- Ej obligatoriskt&lt;/span&gt;</code> inuti fältets label,
                  efter label-namnet för att markera ett valfritt fält.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-8">
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="exampleInputEmail1">Mailadress <span class="text-muted">- Ej obligatoriskt</span></label>
                  <input type="email" class="form-control" id="exampleInputEmail1" aria-describedby="emailHelp" placeholder="Mailadress">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label for="exampleInputEmail1">Text <span class="text-muted">- Ej obligatoriskt</span></label>
                  <input type="email" class="form-control" id="exampleInputEmail1" aria-describedby="emailHelp" placeholder="Text">
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <h5>Form validation</h5>
                <p>Om möjligt (Hej alla utvecklare): Berätta redan innan man trycker på "submit" att något är fel/rätt för att effektivisera flödet för användaren.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-8">
                <div class="form-group has-success">
                  <label class="col-form-label" for="inputSuccess1">Mailadress</label>
                  <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-success" id="inputSuccess1" value="info@significantbit.se">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group has-warning">
                  <label class="col-form-label" for="inputWarning1">Lösenord</label>
                  <input type="password" class="form-control form-control-warning" id="inputWarning1" value="lösen ord">
                  <div class="form-control-feedback">Svagt lösenord!</div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group has-danger">
                  <label class="col-form-label" for="inputDanger1">För- och efternamn</label>
                  <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-danger" id="inputDanger1" value="Anders And3rson">
                  <div class="form-control-feedback">Skriv alltid ut vad som är fel, så användaren förstår vad som behöver göras.</div>
                  <small class="form-text text-muted">Example help text that remains unchanged.</small>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
